<h2><%= @workshop.name %> Workshop Registration</h2>

<h3>First, the basics:</h3>

<p>We swear on our precious magnesium camera bodies that none of the following information will be distributed, sold, published, or looked at sideways. Ever.</p>

<h3>Cost</h3>

<p>The cost of this workshop is <%= number_to_currency(@workshop.cost) %>. You'll be asked to send us your payment via snail mail or over the Internet (through PayPal, etc.) after you've registered. Your seat in the workshop will <strong>not be reserved</strong> until payment is received.</p>

<div class="form_container">

  <% if @student.errors.count > 0 %>
    <div class="error">
      <p>The fields in red are required or their content isn't valid. Make sure you've entered a proper e-mail address and supplied information for all fields.</p>
      <ul>
      <% @student.errors.each do |error| %>
        <li><%= "#{error[0]} #{error[1]}"%></li>
      <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  <% end %>
  
  <% form_tag "/register/create" do %>
    <%= render :partial => 'form' %>
    <%= hidden_field_tag 'workshop', @workshop.id %>
    <div class="form_row"><div class="form_label">&nbsp;</div><div class="form_field"><%= submit_tag "Register" %></div></div>
  <% end %>

</div>
